                <ul>
                    <li>Publish MVP website as a Tor hidden service.  <strong>Status: <span class="highlight">done</span></strong></li>
                    <li>Deploy website on a public web server.  <strong>Status: <span class="highlight">done</span></strong></li>
                    <li>Launch community forums (Tor hidden and public).  <strong>Status: <span class="highlight">done</span></strong></li>
                    <li>Distribute for technical review within cypherpunk and voluntaryist networks.</li>

                </ul>
        <h4>DAO Development</h4>

                <ul>
                    <li>Implement DAO constitution with cypherpunk principles.  <strong>Status: <span class="highlight">in progress</span></strong></li>
                    <li>Architect tiered token distribution with cryptographic soulbound mechanism.</li>
                    <li>Create ERC-20 governance token contracts with permanent rights preservation.</li>
                    <li>Implement hold tracking for 2x rewards.</li>

                </ul>
