                    </label>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Post-launch development focuses on:</p>
                        <ul><li>Expanding exchange trading pairs</li></ul>
                        <ul><li>Implementing network-wide indexing and search functionality</li></ul>
                        <ul><li>Developing client-side social media capabilities</li></ul>
                        <ul><li>Creating the decentralized trading platform for goods and services</li></ul>
                        <ul><li>Implementing anonymous usage capability (network hops)</li></ul>
                        <p>The Community Development Fund ensures ongoing development and governance for years after the initial phases.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
